P_HTM[450]='*132. Ekavidhena viññāṇakkhandho – phassasampayutto.*';
P_HTM[451]='*Duvidhena viññāṇakkhandho – atthi lokiyo, atthi lokuttaro.*';
P_HTM[452]='*Tividhena  viññāṇakkhandho – atthi upādinnupādāniyo, atthi anupādinnupādāniyo, atthi anupādinnaanupādāniyo…pe…. Evaṃ dasavidhena viññāṇakkhandho.*';
P_HTM[453]='*133. Ekavidhena viññāṇakkhandho – phassasampayutto.*';
P_HTM[454]='*Duvidhena viññāṇakkhandho – atthi kenaci viññeyyo, atthi kenaci na viññeyyo.*';
P_HTM[455]='*Tividhena viññāṇakkhandho – atthi saṃkiliṭṭhasaṃkilesiko, atthi asaṃkiliṭṭhasaṃkilesiko, atthi asaṃkiliṭṭhaasaṃkilesiko…pe…. Evaṃ  dasavidhena viññāṇakkhandho.*';
P_HTM[456]='*134. Ekavidhena viññāṇakkhandho – phassasampayutto.*';
P_HTM[457]='*Duvidhena viññāṇakkhandho – atthi sāsavo, atthi anāsavo.*';
P_HTM[458]='*Tividhena  viññāṇakkhandho – atthi savitakkasavicāro, atthi avitakkavicāramatto, atthi avitakkaavicāro…pe…. Evaṃ dasavidhena viññāṇakkhandho.*';
P_HTM[459]='*135. Ekavidhena viññāṇakkhandho – phassasampayutto.*';
P_HTM[460]='*Duvidhena viññāṇakkhandho – atthi āsavasampayutto, atthi āsavavippayutto.*';
P_HTM[461]='*Tividhena viññāṇakkhandho – atthi pītisahagato, atthi sukhasahagato, atthi upekkhāsahagato…pe…. Evaṃ dasavidhena viññāṇakkhandho.*';
P_HTM[462]='*136. Ekavidhena viññāṇakkhandho – phassasampayutto.*';
P_HTM[463]='*Duvidhena viññāṇakkhandho – atthi āsavavippayuttasāsavo, atthi āsavavippayuttaanāsavo.*';
P_HTM[464]='*Tividhena viññāṇakkhandho – atthi dassanena pahātabbo, atthi bhāvanāya pahātabbo, atthi neva dassanena na bhāvanāya pahātabbo…pe…. Evaṃ dasavidhena viññāṇakkhandho.*';
P_HTM[465]='*137. Ekavidhena  viññāṇakkhandho – phassasampayutto.*';
P_HTM[466]='*Duvidhena viññāṇakkhandho – atthi saṃyojaniyo, atthi asaṃyojaniyo.*';
P_HTM[467]='*Tividhena viññāṇakkhandho – atthi dassanena pahātabbahetuko, atthi bhāvanāya pahātabbahetuko, atthi neva dassanena na bhāvanāya pahātabbahetuko…pe…. Evaṃ dasavidhena viññāṇakkhandho.*';
P_HTM[468]='*138. Ekavidhena viññāṇakkhandho – phassasampayutto.*';
P_HTM[469]='*Duvidhena  viññāṇakkhandho – atthi saṃyojanasampayutto, atthi saṃyojanavippayutto.*';
P_HTM[470]='*Tividhena viññāṇakkhandho – atthi ācayagāmī, atthi apacayagāmī, atthi nevācayagāmināpacayagāmī…pe…. Evaṃ dasavidhena viññāṇakkhandho.*';
P_HTM[471]='*139. Ekavidhena viññāṇakkhandho – phassasampayutto.*';
P_HTM[472]='*Duvidhena viññāṇakkhandho – atthi saṃyojanavippayuttasaṃyojaniyo, atthi saṃyojanavippayuttaasaṃyojaniyo.*';
P_HTM[473]='*Tividhena viññāṇakkhandho – atthi sekkho, atthi asekkho, atthi nevasekkhanāsekkho…pe…. Evaṃ dasavidhena viññāṇakkhandho.*';
