P_HTM[482]='*Tividhena viññāṇakkhandho – atthi hīno, atthi majjhimo, atthi paṇīto…pe…. Evaṃ dasavidhena viññāṇakkhandho.*';
P_HTM[483]='*143. Ekavidhena viññāṇakkhandho – phassasampayutto.*';
