P_HTM[485]='*Tividhena viññāṇakkhandho – atthi micchattaniyato, atthi sammattaniyato, atthi aniyato…pe…. Evaṃ dasavidhena viññāṇakkhandho.*';
P_HTM[486]='*144. Ekavidhena viññāṇakkhandho – phassasampayutto.*';
P_HTM[487]='*Duvidhena viññāṇakkhandho – atthi oghasampayutto, atthi oghavippayutto.*';
P_HTM[488]='*Tividhena viññāṇakkhandho – atthi maggārammaṇo, atthi maggahetuko, atthi maggādhipati…pe…. Evaṃ dasavidhena viññāṇakkhandho.*';
P_HTM[489]='*145. Ekavidhena viññāṇakkhandho – phassasampayutto.*';
P_HTM[490]='*Duvidhena viññāṇakkhandho – atthi oghavippayuttaoghaniyo, atthi oghavippayuttaanoghaniyo.*';
P_HTM[491]='*Tividhena viññāṇakkhandho – atthi uppanno, atthi anuppanno, atthi uppādī…pe…. Evaṃ dasavidhena viññāṇakkhandho.*';
P_HTM[492]='*146. Ekavidhena viññāṇakkhandho – phassasampayutto.*';
